Package com.apriori.concurrent.contended

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContendedBoolean
    Like an AtomicBoolean, except uses padding to reduce cache contention (aka false-sharing) with writes to nearby memory locations.
    ContendedInteger
    Like an AtomicInteger, except uses padding to reduce cache contention (aka false-sharing) with writes to nearby memory locations.
    ContendedLong
    Like an AtomicLong, except uses padding to reduce cache contention (aka false-sharing) with writes to nearby memory locations.
    ContendedReference<V>
    Like an AtomicReference, except uses padding to reduce cache contention (aka false-sharing) with writes to nearby memory locations.
